Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,欢迎加入OCR小组 qq群906722936 字幕优先发布于群内 字幕广告招租 商业合作Q:1585235535
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.19,0:00:22.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,《比利小子》前情提要\N{\rYUANWEN}Previously on Billy the Kid
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.48,0:00:24.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不许进入我家中\N{\rYUANWEN}Do not come in my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.86,0:00:26.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们杀了所有人 比利\N{\rYUANWEN}They killed everyone, Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.82,0:00:29.36,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\rYUANWEN}Iknow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.16,0:00:34.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我会为你家人报仇的 我发誓\N{\rYUANWEN}I will avenge your family's death, I swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.91,0:00:39.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好吧 我们要接管这个镇子\N{\rYUANWEN}AII right. We're takin' over the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.41,0:00:41.75,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们要恢复林肯镇的法律和秩序\N{\rYUANWEN}We're gonna restore law and order in Lincoln.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.17,0:00:45.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以我们必须干掉浩世集团\N{\rYUANWEN}But we have to take out The House to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.17,0:00:46.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,看来监管者已经控制了市中心\N{\rYUANWEN}It would seem that The Regulators control
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.67,0:00:48.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,和墨西哥区的大部分地区\N{\rYUANWEN}most of the downtown and the Mexican quarter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.97,0:00:50.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我会叫几个副手过来\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm callin' in my deputies.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.68,0:00:52.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们一到我就让他们去\N{\rYUANWEN}As soon as they arrive, I'll send them
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.80,0:00:53.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,汤斯顿商行\N{\rYUANWEN}to the Tunstall Store.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.93,0:00:55.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,来吧 孩子们\N{\rYUANWEN}Here we go, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.85,0:01:01.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,监管者和墨西哥人\N{\rYUANWEN}The Regulators with the Mexicans
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.19,0:01:03.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,构成了一支65人左右的武装力量\N{\rYUANWEN}constitute a significant force of around 65.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.77,0:01:07.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,可我们还凑不齐三分之一\N{\rYUANWEN}Right now that's a third more than we can muster.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.28,0:01:08.44,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,治安官说的对 比利小子知道我们下落\N{\rYUANWEN}Sheriff's right. If The Kid wants us,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.53,0:01:09.82,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他随时都能找过来\N{\rYUANWEN}he knows where we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.90,0:01:13.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,除非 除非我们剑走偏锋\N{\rYUANWEN}Unless. we change the odds.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.57,0:01:15.87,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,达德利上校 我是新任治安官\N{\rYUANWEN}Colonel Dudley, it's the new sheriff.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.99,0:01:18.41,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我带来一份阿克塞尔\N{\rYUANWEN}I have here a proclamation
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.50,0:01:21.41,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,总督的公告 要求所有武装人员\N{\rYUANWEN}from Governor Axtell. It commands all armed men
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.50,0:01:26.25,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,在美国军队召唤前 就地解散\N{\rYUANWEN}to disband, so long as U. S. Army can be summoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.30,0:01:28.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们决不投降 我现在相信了\N{\rYUANWEN}We must never surrender. I believe that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.92,0:01:32.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们在为正义而战 为崇高的事业而战\N{\rYUANWEN}We're fighting for a good cause, a noble cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.89,0:01:35.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,加勒特治安官 好样的\N{\rYUANWEN}Sheriff Garrett, good man!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.39,0:01:39.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你来得正是时候\N{\rYUANWEN}You came just in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.52,0:01:42.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我命令你们所有人马上回家\N{\rYUANWEN}I am ordering all of you to go home, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.39,0:01:44.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,本镇正在开始宵禁 解禁时间末知\N{\rYUANWEN}This town is under permanent curfew.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.94,0:01:46.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,达德利上校才代表这个国家的真正律法\N{\rYUANWEN}Colonel Dudley is the real law in this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.90,0:01:48.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,只要我们跟他解释\N{\rYUANWEN}And when we explain to him- -
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.48,0:01:49.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不会有什么不同的 麦克斯温太太\N{\rYUANWEN}It won't make any difference, Mrs. McSween.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.78,0:01:55.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你和我 我们是伙伴关系\N{\rYUANWEN}You and me, we're partners here,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.62,0:01:58.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,加勒特治安官 我只有一个愿望\N{\rYUANWEN}and all I want, Sheriff Garrett,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.29,0:02:01.62,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,就是看到那个比利臭小子\N{\rYUANWEN}is nothing more than to see that Billy the fuckin' Kid
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.71,0:02:03.33,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,挂在绞刑架上\N{\rYUANWEN}hangin'on the end of a rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.96,0:03:34.46,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,把那个放楼上去\N{\rYUANWEN}That goes upstairs, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.55,0:03:37.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,小心点 这是我母亲的东西\N{\rYUANWEN}Be careful, it was my mother's.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.65,0:03:56.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,比利 真没有别的办法了么\N{\rYUANWEN}Billy, isn't there something else we can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.78,0:03:58.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们就不能举面白旗\N{\rYUANWEN}I mean, can't we go and take a white flag
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.49,0:03:59.95,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,去找上校谈谈吗\N{\rYUANWEN}and go up and talk to the Colonel?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.03,0:04:01.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你听到了 整个镇子都被封锁 要实行宵禁\N{\rYUANWEN}You heard him. The whole town is on lockdown. It's a curfew.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.99,0:04:03.87,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那我们为什么不离开呢 离开林肯\N{\rYUANWEN}Why don't we try and leave, get out of Lincoln?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.95,0:04:05.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,查理 我们不能再跑了\N{\rYUANWEN}Charlie, we're not runnin' again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.58,0:04:07.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我只是不希望大家惹毛美国军队\N{\rYUANWEN}I just don't want us gettin' cut down in the street
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.46,0:04:09.08,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,被横尸街头 但我们不会放弃的\N{\rYUANWEN}by the U. S. Army, but we're not quittin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.88,0:04:19.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们都会死的 比利\N{\rYUANWEN}Are we all gonna die, Billy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.51,0:04:21.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不会的 汤姆\N{\rYUANWEN}No, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.55,0:04:22.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你怎么能这么肯定\N{\rYUANWEN}How can you be so sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.89,0:04:24.64,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,因为我正竭尽全力\N{\rYUANWEN}Because I'm doin' everything in my power
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.72,0:04:26.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,确保这不会发生\N{\rYUANWEN}to make sure that doesn't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.77,0:04:28.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好了 去帮忙在房子\N{\rYUANWEN}Now, go help put the barricades
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.77,0:04:29.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,南边设置路障\N{\rYUANWEN}in the south side of the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.02,0:04:31.56,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,干点有用的事\N{\rYUANWEN}Make yourself useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.19,0:04:37.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,有人来了\N{\rYUANWEN}Someone's comin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.41,0:04:50.04,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是谁\N{\rYUANWEN}Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.12,0:04:52.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我是克雷医生 还记得我吗\N{\rYUANWEN}It's Dr. Clay. You remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.84,0:04:56.05,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,慢一点\N{\rYUANWEN}Slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.93,0:05:09.35,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,哈 我当然记得\N{\rYUANWEN}Ha. Why, of course I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.43,0:05:11.52,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不介意我们进来吧 麦克斯温先生\N{\rYUANWEN}Mind if we come in, Mr. McSween?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.60,0:05:12.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,当然 请进 请进\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes, come in. Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.94,0:05:16.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,没关系 没关系\N{\rYUANWEN}It's all right. It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.95,0:05:25.62,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,什么风把您吹来了 医生\N{\rYUANWEN}What brings you here, doc?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.70,0:05:27.03,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你好啊 比利\N{\rYUANWEN}Hello, Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.12,0:05:29.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,请允许我介绍一下内人 爱丽丝\N{\rYUANWEN}Uh, may I introduce my wife, Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.45,0:05:31.04,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,她是个护士\N{\rYUANWEN}She's a nurse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.12,0:05:32.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们昨天听到些消息 觉得可能会有麻烦\N{\rYUANWEN}We've come because we listened to what was said yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.88,0:05:34.63,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以才过来的\N{\rYUANWEN}and think there might be trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.71,0:05:37.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如果真是这样 你可能会需要我们\N{\rYUANWEN}In which case, you might need us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.96,0:05:40.55,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你们确定要以身涉险吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Are you sure you want to put yourself in the way of danger?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.63,0:05:42.05,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,让我来说吧 麦克斯温先生\N{\rYUANWEN}If I can speak for both of us, Mr. McSween,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.13,0:05:43.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们站在你这边\N{\rYUANWEN}we are on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.89,0:05:46.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们相信监管者 相信你们的大业\N{\rYUANWEN}We believe in The Regulators and in your cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.81,0:05:48.64,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们不能袖手旁观 什么也不做\N{\rYUANWEN}We simply could not stand by and do nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.68,0:05:52.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 谢谢两位\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, thank you...both.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.27,0:05:58.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,克雷医生 我来帮您拿帽子 愿上帝保佑你\N{\rYUANWEN}Dr. Clay. Let me take your hat. God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.07,0:06:00.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢了\N{\rYUANWEN}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.72,0:06:26.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,朋友们\N{\rYUANWEN}Friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.55,0:06:28.01,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们仍需要加强\N{\rYUANWEN}we still need to tighten
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.10,0:06:30.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,对监管者据点的包围\N{\rYUANWEN}the ring around The Regulators' stronghold,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.56,0:06:33.14,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,也就是麦克斯温大宅\N{\rYUANWEN}which is to say, McSween's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.19,0:06:35.06,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们可不想让任何一人逃走 好吗\N{\rYUANWEN}We don't want any of them slippin' away, do we?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.15,0:06:37.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,同时 在我的敦促下\N{\rYUANWEN}Meanwhile, with my encouragement,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.86,0:06:40.44,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,加勒特治安官拿到了逮捕麦克斯温\N{\rYUANWEN}Sheriff Garrett has obtained fresh warrants
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.53,0:06:42.03,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,比利小子和其他监管者的\N{\rYUANWEN}for the arrest of McSween, Billy the Kid and the rest
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.11,0:06:43.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,逮捕令\N{\rYUANWEN}of The Regulators
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.78,0:06:46.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,原因是涉嫌共谋杀害布雷迪治安官\N{\rYUANWEN}for complicity in the murder of Sheriff Brady.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.20,0:06:48.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,现在 看在新任治安官的份上\N{\rYUANWEN}Now, for the sake of our new sheriff,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.53,0:06:50.16,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们得去执行这张搜查令\N{\rYUANWEN}we're gonna try to serve these warrants,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.24,0:06:51.79,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,因为从今往后 一切行为都要在法律\N{\rYUANWEN}because everything now has got to be done within the letter
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.87,0:06:53.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,允许的范围内进行\N{\rYUANWEN}of the fuckin'law.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.54,0:06:54.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们也绝不会做什么违法的事\N{\rYUANWEN}We wouldn't dream of doing anything unlawful,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.00,0:06:56.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,对吗 小子们\N{\rYUANWEN}now would we, boys?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.08,0:06:58.67,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,地狱会让他绝望的\N{\rYUANWEN}Ain't no hope in hell
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.75,0:07:00.67,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,比利会投降的\N{\rYUANWEN}Billy is just gonna surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.75,0:07:02.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这得他来决定 不是吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, that's up to him, now, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:05.63,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他要是不这么做 就是真的傻\N{\rYUANWEN}He would be a fool not to, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.72,0:07:08.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,杰西 来一下\N{\rYUANWEN}Jesse, come.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.18,0:07:09.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我亲自把达德利上校\N{\rYUANWEN}I personally invited
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.89,0:07:11.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,从军营里请来\N{\rYUANWEN}Colonel Dudley out of his shite tent
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.06,0:07:13.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,下榻进这里的客房\N{\rYUANWEN}to stay in one of the guest rooms here,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.93,0:07:16.64,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,毕竟客房要比帐篷舒服多了\N{\rYUANWEN}where he's gonna be far more comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.36,0:07:21.07,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你觉得上校站在我们这边吗\N{\rYUANWEN}You think the Colonel is on our side?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.15,0:07:23.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,加勒特治安官\N{\rYUANWEN}Sheriff Garrett asked him down
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.78,0:07:25.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是代表法制派请他出山\N{\rYUANWEN}on behalf of the Law and Order Party,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.61,0:07:26.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,来解决这个问题的 所以没错\N{\rYUANWEN}to sort this thing out, so yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.07,0:07:29.16,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我觉得他会站我们这边\N{\rYUANWEN}I figure that's where his sympathies lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.30,0:07:51.55,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,达德利上校 早上好\N{\rYUANWEN}Colonel Dudley, good mornin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.64,0:07:53.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,治安官 谢谢你们\N{\rYUANWEN}Sheriff. Thank you, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.77,0:07:57.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,莱利先生邀请我住进家里\N{\rYUANWEN}Mr. Riley has kindly invited me to stay at the House.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.35,0:08:01.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他真是太有心了\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, that is, uh, mighty civil of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.07,0:08:05.23,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我想请你帮个忙\N{\rYUANWEN}I have a favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.32,0:08:07.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,又要帮忙 治安官\N{\rYUANWEN}Another, Sheriff?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.20,0:08:08.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我有一张麦克斯温先生\N{\rYUANWEN}I have some warrants to serve
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.74,0:08:11.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,和监管者成员的逮捕令\N{\rYUANWEN}on Mr. McSween and members of The Regulators,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.20,0:08:14.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,理由是他们涉嫌谋杀我的上一任\N{\rYUANWEN}for their role in the murder of my predecessor.
