Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.14,0:42:34.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你今天很勇敢\N{\rYUANWEN}You were brave today.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.35,0:42:38.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我想要讨回正义\N{\rYUANWEN}I wanted justice.
