Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.60,0:44:43.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢您\N{\rYUANWEN}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.06,0:44:46.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,祝您一路平安 再见\N{\rYUANWEN}Have a safe journey, and farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.19,0:44:47.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\rYUANWEN}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.48,0:44:54.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,二位早上好啊\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, top of the mornin' to you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.07,0:44:57.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你闻到了吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Do you smell that?
