Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.34,0:45:19.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,绝不会被这种人渣吓倒\N{\rYUANWEN}Not by scum like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.26,0:45:21.05,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那您打算做什么 夫人\N{\rYUANWEN}So what are you going to do, Senora?
