Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.52,0:45:31.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,为我丈夫讨回公道\N{\rYUANWEN}and bring justice to my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.27,0:45:34.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他一直都相信 真理和正义必胜\N{\rYUANWEN}He always believed that truth and justice will prevail,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.36,0:45:35.32,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我也是\N{\rYUANWEN}and so do I.
