Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.35,0:46:47.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,治安官\N{\rYUANWEN}Sheriff.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.35,0:46:50.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,没想到会有这么多人的生命毁于一旦\N{\rYUANWEN}I had not thought to see so many lives undone.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.73,0:46:54.44,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这就是我们林肯人的作风\N{\rYUANWEN}That has been the way of it here in Lincoln.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.24,0:47:03.41,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,可怜的贝克维斯\N{\rYUANWEN}Poor Beckwith
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.45,0:47:07.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你知道是谁杀了他 对吧\N{\rYUANWEN}You know who killed him, don't you?
