Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.54,0:47:13.62,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\rYUANWEN}Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.09,0:47:18.42,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你一点都不伤心吗 杰西\N{\rYUANWEN}Ain't you got any feelings, Jesse?
