Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.47,0:47:26.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我要是死了 他也不会伤心的 对吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Like, he wouldn't have any feelings for me, now would he?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.26,0:47:28.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他当然会\N{\rYUANWEN}Yeah, sure he would.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.39,0:47:29.35,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不会\N{\rYUANWEN}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.52,0:47:35.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们唯一的相同之处 就是金钱\N{\rYUANWEN}Only thing we all have in common is money.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.94,0:47:39.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,把感情抛在脑后 我们才能成功\N{\rYUANWEN}We leave our feelings behind so we can make it.
