Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.04,0:47:52.04,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你不喜欢钱吗 杰西\N{\rYUANWEN}You don't like money, Jesse?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.12,0:47:55.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,说什么傻话 奥林杰\N{\rYUANWEN}Don't be stupid, Olinger.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.34,0:47:59.46,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,小心安葬他\N{\rYUANWEN}You be careful with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.13,0:48:05.05,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,既然那些罪犯已被赶走\N{\rYUANWEN}Now that you've flushed these criminals out,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.14,0:48:07.51,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,治安官 是时候翻过这一篇\N{\rYUANWEN}Sheriff, it's time to press on,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.60,0:48:09.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,画上句点了\N{\rYUANWEN}get the job done.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.02,0:48:13.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,至于我 我觉得自己这个中间人\N{\rYUANWEN}As for myself, I feel like I have been an honest broker
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.52,0:48:15.14,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,当得还算成功 我已经命令部队\N{\rYUANWEN}in this situation. And I have already
