Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.07,0:48:21.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢您的帮助 上校\N{\rYUANWEN}I appreciate all the help, Colonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.24,0:48:22.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,别担心 我们会\N{\rYUANWEN}And fear not, we will find
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.69,0:48:24.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,追踪并逮捕那些漏网之鱼的\N{\rYUANWEN}and arrest the remaining criminals.
